  "detailed_description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Adventure game meets Point-N-Click and Beat 'Em Up</h2></strong><br><br>Scrap Riders is a pixel art adventure game set in a futuristic cyberpunk universe.<br>You are Rast, a member of the outlaw biker gang called the Scrap Riders.<br>Fight your way through the wastelands and large corporate-controlled metropolises.<br>Embody this smuggler with a caustic sense of humor to survive in this post-apocalyptic world...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Old-school adventure.<br></li><li>Dialogs brimming with biting humor.<br></li><li>A Beat 'em up style that blends investigation and adventure.<br></li><li>The evolution and progression of your character. A rich story, endowed with deep Lore.<br></li><li>Original music composed specifically for Scrap Riders.<br></li><li>Cunning puzzles.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1542550/extras/3f39dcaac2803487d062f058524341d8.poster.avif?t=1680272096\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1542550/extras/3f39dcaac2803487d062f058524341d8.webm?t=1680272096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1542550/extras/3f39dcaac2803487d062f058524341d8.mp4?t=1680272096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ACERBIC POST-APOCALYPTIC HUMOR</h2><br>The world is a cruel place where only the powerful enjoy privileges. To be free, you must live in the wastelands. And resources there are few…<br>Meet with other members of your gang and talk to village inhabitants. <br><br>Eliminate rival gangs and corrupt police officers to accomplish the missions that will earn you greater street cred with the SCRAP RIDERS.<br>Ride your motorcycle and fight for the survival of your gang. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1542550/extras/a69b362e81c11c0113a580859defc88f.poster.avif?t=1680272096\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1542550/extras/a69b362e81c11c0113a580859defc88f.webm?t=1680272096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1542550/extras/a69b362e81c11c0113a580859defc88f.mp4?t=1680272096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Investigate and uncover the conspiracy behind the cargo thefts. <br>But above all, be strong!",
  "about_the_game": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Adventure game meets Point-N-Click and Beat 'Em Up</h2></strong><br><br>Scrap Riders is a pixel art adventure game set in a futuristic cyberpunk universe.<br>You are Rast, a member of the outlaw biker gang called the Scrap Riders.<br>Fight your way through the wastelands and large corporate-controlled metropolises.<br>Embody this smuggler with a caustic sense of humor to survive in this post-apocalyptic world...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Old-school adventure.<br></li><li>Dialogs brimming with biting humor.<br></li><li>A Beat 'em up style that blends investigation and adventure.<br></li><li>The evolution and progression of your character. A rich story, endowed with deep Lore.<br></li><li>Original music composed specifically for Scrap Riders.<br></li><li>Cunning puzzles.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1542550/extras/3f39dcaac2803487d062f058524341d8.poster.avif?t=1680272096\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1542550/extras/3f39dcaac2803487d062f058524341d8.webm?t=1680272096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1542550/extras/3f39dcaac2803487d062f058524341d8.mp4?t=1680272096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ACERBIC POST-APOCALYPTIC HUMOR</h2><br>The world is a cruel place where only the powerful enjoy privileges. To be free, you must live in the wastelands. And resources there are few…<br>Meet with other members of your gang and talk to village inhabitants. <br><br>Eliminate rival gangs and corrupt police officers to accomplish the missions that will earn you greater street cred with the SCRAP RIDERS.<br>Ride your motorcycle and fight for the survival of your gang. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1542550/extras/a69b362e81c11c0113a580859defc88f.poster.avif?t=1680272096\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1542550/extras/a69b362e81c11c0113a580859defc88f.webm?t=1680272096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1542550/extras/a69b362e81c11c0113a580859defc88f.mp4?t=1680272096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Investigate and uncover the conspiracy behind the cargo thefts. <br>But above all, be strong!",
